            "body": "In general it's a known issue that during startup, messages might not display and/or highlight.\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/16750\r\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/8676#issuecomment-487357807\r\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/21178\r\n\r\n\r\nLong-term solution is likely to \"queue\" messages so that their display does not depend on stale screen state: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/22478",
