            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Yes. This issue only reproduce on startup.\r\nThe `Error detected while processing` message is printed in `do_exrc_initialization`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/e5f4394eb7a27a9e5eaab088e6acf5553c64cf59/src/nvim/main.c#L2046-L2061\r\n\r\nHow about concat `Error detected while processing` and `err.msg` into one line? Like `semsg(\"Error detected while processing %s: %s\", VIMRC_LUA_FILE, err.msg)`.",
